Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.96,0:21:40.75,AitakuteRomaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}ima kimi wa doko ni iru no nani shite'ru no
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.46,0:21:50.35,AitakuteRomaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}kami{\fsp-2\fs40}- {\fsp\fs}sama ni negai todoku nara mō ichido dake
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.97,0:21:57.81,AitakuteRomaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}aitakute kimi ni aitakute
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.31,0:22:06.78,AitakuteRomaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}ima mo kono mune wa kimi{\fsp-2\fs40}- {\fsp\fs}iro ni somaru (dakishimetakute)
